'''阿马拉瓦蒂'''（[[英语|英语]]：Amaravati）是[[印度|印度]][[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]的一个正在新建中的城市<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://surbanajurong.com/sector/amaravati-capital-city-of-andhra-pradesh/?lang=zh-hans |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170327075828/https://surbanajurong.com/sector/amaravati-capital-city-of-andhra-pradesh/?lang=zh-hans |archive-date=2017-03-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，建设区域位于[[奎师那河|奎师那河]]南岸的[[贡土尔县|贡土尔县]]，是实际上[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]的新首府。

==地名==

阿马拉瓦蒂在[[梵语|梵语]]和[[泰卢固语|泰卢固语]]中意为「神之居所」。

==历史==

阿马拉瓦蒂曾名陀尼耶迦多迦，公元2世纪曾是[[百乘王朝|百乘王朝]]的国都。由于此地拥有举世闻名的佛塔和许多属于公元前2世纪的古迹古物，故成为重要的历史中心<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fojiaolvyou.com/n-135-%E9%98%BF%E9%A9%AC%E6%8B%89%E7%93%A6%E8%92%82%EF%BC%88Amaravati%EF%BC%89.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160803174334/http://www.fojiaolvyou.com/n-135-%E9%98%BF%E9%A9%AC%E6%8B%89%E7%93%A6%E8%92%82%EF%BC%88Amaravati%EF%BC%89.html |archive-date=2016-08-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

[[File:Exhibits_in_the_Museum._permitted_to_take_photos_(2).JPG|thumb]]

[[玄奘|玄奘]]曾于公元640年到访阿马拉瓦蒂，在此停留并研究[[论藏|阿毘达磨藏]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.odiseos.net/XTWeb/index.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2003-02-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20030207040625/http://www.odiseos.net/XTWeb/index.html |archivedate=2003-02-07 }}</ref>。

根据2014年的{{le|2014安得拉邦重组法令|Andhra Pradesh Reorganisation Act, 2014|安得拉邦重组法令}}，[[特伦甘纳邦|特伦甘纳邦]]自[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]析出，安得拉邦首府仍留在已属[[特伦甘纳邦|特伦甘纳邦]]的[[海得拉巴_(印度)|海德拉巴]]。

2015年10月22日，现任印度总理[[纳伦德拉·莫迪|纳伦德拉·莫迪]]、[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]首席部长N. Chandrababu Naidu、[[特伦甘纳邦首席部长列表|特伦甘纳邦首席部长]]{{Link-en|K·钱德拉塞卡·拉奥|Kalvakuntla Chandrashekar Rao}}、日本[[经济产业省|经济产业副大臣]]高木阳介、[[新加坡贸易和工业部|新加坡贸易和工业部长]]S. Iswaran等政要为新城市开建奠基<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/thousands-descend-on-andhra-village-uddandarayunipalem-to-watch-history-in-making/articleshow/49491280.cms |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-03-26 |archive-date=2017-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170802171743/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/thousands-descend-on-andhra-village-uddandarayunipalem-to-watch-history-in-making/articleshow/49491280.cms |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.deccanherald.com/content/506499/andhra-cm-scales-down-amaravathi.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-03-26 |archive-date=2018-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180708133353/https://www.deccanherald.com/content/506499/andhra-cm-scales-down-amaravathi.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年4月开始，[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]首席部长N Chandrababu Naidu在阿马拉瓦蒂办公；2016年10月，[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]的大部分部门和政府官员迁到位于阿马拉瓦蒂的{{Link-en|安得拉邦秘书处|Andhra Pradesh Secretariat}}办公，仅在[[海得拉巴_(印度)|海德拉巴]]留一名骨干人员<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report-andhra-pradesh-secretariat-starts-functioning-from-interim-government-complex-at-amaravati-2260970 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-03-26 |archive-date=2017-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170802182034/http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report-andhra-pradesh-secretariat-starts-functioning-from-interim-government-complex-at-amaravati-2260970 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2017年3月6日，[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]新的立法议会在阿马拉瓦蒂开始运作<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gulte.com/news/56377/After-2200-Years-Amaravati-Gets-Back-Power |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-03-26 |archive-date=2020-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200422004048/https://www.gulte.com/news/56377/After-2200-Years-Amaravati-Gets-Back-Power |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==地理==

[[File:Andhra_Pradeah_Capital_Region.jpg|thumb]]和克利须那县]]

阿马拉瓦蒂位于[[奎师那河|奎师那河]]南岸，属[[贡土尔县|贡土尔县]]，北距[[贡土尔|贡土尔]]24千米，西南距[[维杰亚瓦达|维杰亚瓦达]]12千米。

阿马拉瓦蒂是一个城市通知区（Urban Notified Area），规划发展由{{le|安得拉邦首府圈发展局|Andhra Pradesh Capital Region Development Authority|安得拉邦首府圈发展局}}执行。首府圈面积217.23km²，目前拟建的土地覆盖30个村庄，面积超过14,000公顷<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.economist.com/news/asia/21679822-floods-should-be-warning-those-building-state-capital-scratch-next-time-water |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-03-26 |archive-date=2017-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701161301/http://www.economist.com/news/asia/21679822-floods-should-be-warning-those-building-state-capital-scratch-next-time-water |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==经济==

安得拉邦首府圈主要的经济产业是[[农业|农业]]、[[贸易|商业贸易]]和[[纺织业|纺织业]]，农业以其出口的[[辣椒|辣椒]]、[[棉花|棉花]]和[[烟草|烟草]]而闻名。

==交通==

[[File:Amaravathi_road_in_Penumaka.jpg|thumb]]

印度[[国道5号_(印度)|16号国道]]经过附近<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thehansindia.com/posts/index/Andhra-Pradesh/2016-06-22/AP-CM-to-take-part-in-Iftar-party-/236789 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-03-26 |archive-date=2018-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180620153101/http://www.thehansindia.com/posts/index/Andhra-Pradesh/2016-06-22/AP-CM-to-take-part-in-Iftar-party-/236789 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。目前拟建全长105km的铁路连接阿马拉瓦蒂与[[维杰亚瓦达|维杰亚瓦达]]、[[贡土尔|贡土尔]]、[[泰纳利|泰纳利]]等城市，投资超过15亿美元<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Vijayawada/Circular-rail-line-for-Amaravati-approved/article16806688.ece |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-03-26 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713182204/https://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Vijayawada/Circular-rail-line-for-Amaravati-approved/article16806688.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[维杰亚瓦达机场|维杰亚瓦达机场]]服务阿马拉瓦蒂，正逐渐升级为国际机场<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guntur.nic.in/reports/nelapadu_sia.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170227232609/http://www.guntur.nic.in/reports/nelapadu_sia.pdf |archive-date=2017-02-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

